Package com.GREENWORKS.eco.data

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Admin
    The Admin class is for handling admin related database transactions.
    Data
    The purpose that the Data class fulfills is to provide the front-end of the application with all of the necessary information.
    DatabaseCleaner
    This class will remove redundant points from the locations table and put them in the problem_locations table.
    EventPin
    The Event class definition.
    GenericPin
    This is meant to logically represent a generic point of data.
    LocationPin
    Child class definition of Location.
    OldEventPin
    The OldEventPin is meant to logically represent events that haved aged past their date.
    Pillar
    The class definition for the Pillar object.
    Pin
    The parent abstract class for all Pin related data.
    PinFactory
    Abstract factory that is used to instantiate and return any of the priority level ToDoItem objects.
    ProblemPin
    This is the ProblemPin class.
    SessionAssistant
    This class is intended to assist the Servlets by providing a medium for all the backend database functions.
    SessionFactoryUtility
    The definition of the SessionFactoryUtility class.
    SubPillar
    The class definition for the SubPillar object.
